    • Class Entity extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • shape

          java.awt.Shape shape
          The Shape object representing the appearance and collision box of this Entity.

        • grid

          Spacetime grid
          The Spacetime object to which this Entity belongs.

        • path

          QuadTreePath path
          An index used by the QuadTree in the Spacetime grid to quickly locate the quadrant in which this Entity is currently located.

        • x

          double x
          The Entity's x-coordinate, representing the centre of its shape.

        • y

          double y
          The Entity's y-coordinate, representing the centre of its shape.

        • theta

          double theta
          The Entity's current angle, in radians. 0 rad is pointing right. 1/2 pi rad is pointing down (since y coordinates increase downwards). Pi rad is pointing left. 3/2 pi rad is pointing up.

        • anchorX

          double anchorX
          The x-coordinate of the rotational center for this Entity. This coordinate is relative to the Entity's x-coordinate. By default, this value is set to 0.

        • anchorY

          double anchorY
          The y-coordinate of the rotational center for this Entity. This coordinate is relative to the Entity's y-coordinate. By default, this value is set to 0.

        • offsetX

          double offsetX
          The x-coordinate offset for the Shape of this Entity. This is relative to the Entity's x-coordinate.

        • offsetY

          double offsetY
          The y-coordinate offset for the Shape of this Entity. This is relative to the Entity's y-coordinate.

        • friction

          double friction
          Determines the velocity and angular velocity decrease that occurs at the end of every tick. 0 indicates no decrease (frictionless). 1 indicates immediate nullification of velocities (high friction).

        • velocity

          Vector2D velocity
          The current velocity of this Entity. The x-component represents the change in x-coordinate per tick, and the y-component represents the change in y-coordinate per tick.

        • angularVelocity

          double angularVelocity
          The rate by which this Entity rotates every tick. For example, if angularVelocity were pi/4, this Entity would rotate by pi/4 radians every tick.

    • Class QuadBranch extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • leaves

          java.util.List<E> leaves
          A list of all of the Entities that are entirely enclosed by this QuadBranch.

        • noncommittals

          java.util.List<E> noncommittals
          A list of all of the Entities that are only partially in this QuadBranch.

        • parent

          QuadBranch parent
          The parent QuadBranch of this QuadBranch, or null if there is no parent.

        • children

          QuadBranch[] children
          The four children QuadBranches of this QuadBranch, or null if there are no children.

        • maxSize

          int maxSize
          The maximum number of Entities that can be held by this QuadBranch before it divides. This value includes both Entities that are entirely enclosed by this QuadBranch as well as noncommittal Entities that are only partially in this QuadBranch.

        • maxDepth

          int maxDepth
          The maximum depth that this QuadBranch structure will go before ceasing to divide any further.

        • depth

          int depth
          The current depth of this QuadBranch. A QuadBranch will have a depth value 1 greater than that of its parent. For example, a root QuadBranch will always start with depth = 0, so all of its children QuadBranches have depth = 1.

        • size

          int size
          The number of Entities and noncommittal Entities held by this QuadBranch. This does not include any Entities in any children QuadBranches.

        • bounds

          Box bounds
          The Box representing the boundaries of this QuadBranch.

        • path

          QuadTreePath path
          The QuadTreePath to this QuadBranch.

        • hasChildren

          boolean hasChildren
          Is true if this QuadBranch has children QuadBranches; false otherwise

    • Class Spacetime extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • tick

          long tick
          The time stamp of this simulation

        • size

          java.awt.Dimension size
          The size of this Spacetime grid, in units of TerrainTile widths.

        • shake

          double shake
          The Graphics object in draw(Graphics2D) is offset by a random value ranging from 0 to this value every time this Spacetime is drawn, thus resulting in a cool shaking effect. Default value is 0.

        • shakeDecrement

          double shakeDecrement
          The decrease that the shake variable undergoes every tick. This only applies when shake is greater than 0.

        • fadeTicks

          int fadeTicks
          The number of ticks it takes for a special effect to fade away.

        • layers

          java.util.List<E> layers
          The layers of this Spacetime.

        • removalQueue

          java.util.List<E> removalQueue
          A list of Entities that are to be removed at the beginning of the next tick.

        • incubator

          Incubator incubator
          The incubator responsible for this Spacetime.
